    "creation_date" : 1318688928,
    "answer_id" : 7778415,
    "question_id" : 5054132,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<pre><code>public String getGermanCurrencyFormat(double value) {\n    NumberFormat nf = NumberFormat.getNumberInstance(Locale.GERMAN);\n    nf.setGroupingUsed(true);\n    return \"€ \" + nf.format(value);\n}\n</code></pre>\n"
  }, {
